The entrapment efficiency of dyes was measured via a reported protocol66,67. We measured the absorbance of PdTPBP or perylene in dichloromethane (A0) before synthesis of the TTA-UCNP. We added the dichloromethane to extract the PdTPBP and the perylene from the final TTA-UCNP product to attain absorbance (A) for PdTPBP or perylene in the TTA-UCNP. Then the entrapment efficiency of PdTPBP or perylene was calculated according to Eq. (2), which has been used similarly in the literature66,67.2Entrapmentefficiency%=A/A0×100\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
